Information gathering is the first phase of any penetration test
What technologies are being used? What vulnerabilities exist? More about the IP address
Passive information gathering gaining as much knowledge as possible without engaging with the target
active information gathering  as much knowledge as possible while engaging with the target <-- this phase requires authorization

Passive information gathering:
ip addresses dns info
domain names and domain ownership
email addresses and social media
web technologies
Sub domains

Active information gathering
discovering open ports
Infastructure of a target network
Enumeration information
